                        <li><img src="images/tick.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">Get your game server up and running in less than a minute.</li>
                        <li><img src="images/tick.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">Want to do a test run? Try our 10-day free trial!</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="gameservers.html" class="button">Get Started</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col" id="hiw-img">
                    <img src="images/get-started.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



    <section class="grey-bg" id="home-games">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="title">
