    <section class="blue-bg promobar" id="promobarfix">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="flex-grid">
                <div class="col">
                    <h2>10%</h2>
                    <h3>Off your <br>first month</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col leftauto" id="coupon-code">
                    Use coupon code during checkout: <strong>1STMONTH</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="col leftauto">
                    <div id="timer">
                        <div id="clock"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

        <section class="four-feats" id="home-feats">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="title">
                <h2><small>Included Features</small>Affordable Game Hosting</h2>
                <p>We did the math. By renting a dedicated game server on AleForge, you can have the best of both worlds: inexpensive game hosting services combined with intuitive defense systems and phenomenal performance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grid three">
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/security.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>Unparalleled Security</h4>
                    <p>Protections are included by default in all of our products to ensure your gaming remains shielded from hacks, DDoS, or other malicious acts.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/low-latency.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>Low Latency</h4>
                    <p>Our systems are optimized for performance, processing high volumes of data in real-time with minimal delay.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/never.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>Never Oversold</h4>
                    <p>We have the superior bandwidth and hardware you need to run a quality server and are continuously growing our platform.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/ddos-protection.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>Free DDoS Protection</h4>
                    <p>Sophisticated protection services mean you never have to worry about a distributed denial-of-service attack.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/support.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>24/7 Technical Support</h4>
                    <p>If you want your problem solved without needing multiple support requests, our support agents are ready to assist from debugging crashes, to helping install mods, and more!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <img src="images/servers-added.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                    <h4>Enterprise Hardware</h4>
                    <p>We spec our game servers to provide a minimum clock speed of 3.8 GHz backed with NvME SSD drives to provide the fastest gaming experience around.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-grid one">
                <div class="col">
                    <h5>Are we missing something?</h5>
                    <a href="https://billing.aleforge.net/submitticket.php?step=2&deptid=1" class="button">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
    
