                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="flex-grid one">
                            <div class="col slider">
                                <img src="images/quote-white.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                                <p>"Quick response given the time Zone differences also I was only really expecting general advice To see where my issue may be stemming from I had not actually expected someone to look into the issue very deeply. Very grateful. found issue and have been able to remove it and continue my merry way.”</p>
