    <section class="infastructure">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="title">
                <h2>Infrastructure Overview</h2>
                <form>
                    <select id='tabselect'>
                        <option value='0'>Server Locations</option>
                        <option value='1'>Easy-To-Use Control Panels</option>
                        <option value='2'>Free DDoS Protection</option>
                    </select>
                </form>
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs inf-tabs clearfix" role="tablist" id="home-tabs">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-1" role="tab" class="nav-link active">Server Locations</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-2" role="tab" class="nav-link">Easy-To-Use Control Panel</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tabs-3" role="tab" class="nav-link">Free DDoS Protection</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-content">
                <div class="tab-pane active" id="tabs-1" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="flex-grid two" id="locations">
                        <div class="col">
                            <sergey-import src="map" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col" id="tc-r">
                            <h2>Multiple Locations</h2>
                            <p>We use a global network with reliable facilities and actual redundancy to provide you with 99.9% uptime for uninterrupted game play.</p>
                            <a href="about" class="button">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane" id="tabs-2" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="flex-grid two" id="home-panels">
                        <div class="col" id="tc-l">
                            <h2>Powerful Control Panel</h2>
                            <p>Manage your server and find what you need quickly and easily with our refined game server control panel, complete with mod installer, auto backups, and more.</p>
                            <p>*GameDash panel will be available once it has launched.</p>
                            <div class="flex-grid two" id="cp-half">
                                <div class="col">
                                    <h5>Mod Installers</h5>
                                    <p>Easily install Steam Workshop content, modpacks, plugins, and many more.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col">
                                    <h5>Powerful Interface</h5>
                                    <p>Easy to use for both novice and power users.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <img src="images/panel-preview.webp" loading="lazy" alt="" id="panel">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane" id="tabs-3" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="flex-grid twothirds" id="ddos">
                        <div class="col colsecond" id="ddos-img">
                            <img src="images/ddosicon.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col colfirst" id="tc-r">
                            <h2>DDoS Protection 40 Gbps and Up</h2>
                            <p>We protect you against threats ranging from basic UDP floods to targeted Source Engine Query attacks. The majority of modern threats target application-specific exploits instead of utilizing bandwidth capacity. Our security uses machine learning, actively adjusting as necessary to keep threats out and you in the game.</p>
                            <ul class="checklist">
                                <li><img src="images/tick.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">Customized threat mitigation for every game.</li>
                                <li><img src="images/tick.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">Machine learning threat mitigation applied in real time.</li>
                                <li><img src="images/tick.webp" loading="lazy" alt="">Distributed protection to prevent single points of failure.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



		<Footer />
